HEADWORD: Intercolline
<hw>In`ter*col"line</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Geol.)</fld>
<def>Situated between hills; -- applied especially to valleys lying
between volcanic cones.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

